      "foundryImg": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/TheGiddyLimit/homebrew-img/refs/heads/main/img/CrookedMoon24/Foundry/Subclass/Cleric/Harvest%20Domain%20Spells.webp"
    },
    {
      "ENG_name": "Blessing of the Seasons",
      "name": "四时祝福",
      "source": "CrookedMoon24",
      "page": 73,
      "className": "牧师",
      "classSource": "XPHB",
      "subclassShortName": "收获",
      "subclassSource": "crookedmoon24",
      "level": 6,
      "header": 2,
      "entries": [
        "你可以引导丰收循环之力来化解潜在的灾难。当你周边30尺范围内一个你可见的生物失败于一次豁免检定（该豁免的类型取决于你当前的化身）时，你可以使用{@variantrule 反应|XPHB}来允许其重掷该{@dice d20}并使用新的结果。你可以影响的豁免检定类型如下：",
        {
          "ENG_name": "Sowing",
          "name": "播种",
          "type": "entries",
          "entries": [
            "敏捷和魅力"
          ]
        },
        {
          "ENG_name": "Growing",
          "name": "生长",
          "type": "entries",
          "entries": [
            "体质和智力"
          ]
        },
        {
          "ENG_name": "Reaping",
          "name": "收割",
          "type": "entries",
          "entries": [
            "感知和力量"
          ]
        },
        "此外，无论该豁免检定成功还是失败，掷数量等于你{@variantrule 熟练|XPHB|熟练加值}的d4骰。目标恢复等于结果总值的{@variantrule 生命值|XPHB}。",
        "你可以使用该特性的次数等同于你的感知调整值（最少 1 次）。你在完成一次{@variantrule 长休|XPHB}时重获所有已消耗的使用次数。"
      ],
      "foundryImg": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/TheGiddyLimit/homebrew-img/refs/heads/main/img/CrookedMoon24/Foundry/Subclass/Cleric/Blessing%20of%20the%20Seasons.webp"
    },
    {
      "ENG_name": "Eternal Wheel",
      "name": "永恒之轮",
      "source": "CrookedMoon24",
      "page": 73,
      "className": "牧师",
      "classSource": "XPHB",
      "subclassShortName": "收获",
      "subclassSource": "crookedmoon24",
      "level": 17,
      "header": 2,
      "entries": [
        "当你使用你的{@subclassFeature 五谷丰登|牧师|XPHB|收获|crookedmoon24|3|crookedmoon24}时，你可以唤起生命、死亡且重生的无尽循环，为你自己以及受你的{@classFeature 引导神力|牧师|XPHB|2}影响的生物提供基于你当前化身的一项额外增益：",
        {
          "ENG_name": "Sowing",
          "name": "播种",
          "type": "entries",
          "entries": [
            "目标获得{@spell 再生术|XPHB}的效应，持续1分钟，或直至你失去{@status 专注|XPHB}。"
          ]
        },
        {
          "ENG_name": "Growing",
          "name": "生长",
          "type": "entries",
          "entries": [
            "目标在豁免检定和属性检定中具有{@variantrule 优势|XPHB}，持续1小时或直至你失去{@status 专注|XPHB}（如同{@status 专注|XPHB|专注于}一个法术）。"
          ]
        },
        {
          "ENG_name": "Reaping",
          "name": "收割",
          "type": "entries",
          "entries": [
            "目标获得{@variantrule 抗性|XPHB}对暗蚀、心灵且毒素伤害的抗性，持续1小时。"
          ]
        },
        "一旦你使用了此特性，则直至你完成一次{@variantrule 长休|XPHB}前，都无法再次使用。你也可以消耗一枚七环或更高环阶的法术位（无需动作）来复原该特性的使用次数。"
      ],
      "foundryImg": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/TheGiddyLimit/homebrew-img/refs/heads/main/img/CrookedMoon24/Foundry/Subclass/Cleric/Eternal%20Wheel.webp"
    }
